page.title: 13SEASHORE
page.content: The seashore is quite nice .Some of the beaches have lots of stones and some are sandy . On the beach you can sometimes find coins .When I go to the beach I usually see people with a metal detectors .There are lots of things to do on the beach _you can swim ,play football and can look for crabs in the small rock pools . When the tide is in I go fishing off the coast .Some people go bird watching_some have picnics on the cliffs .The rocks are quite dangerous,some people have fallen off them and been killed
